        "post-content": "Welcome to the new blog The Real Blog\n<h2 class=\"blog-title-main\" style=\"font-size: 1.9em; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #2563eb;\">\n  Why This Blog Exists\n</h2>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-intro\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #1f2937;\">\n  This blog is a public log of what I\u2019m building, learning, and breaking.\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-red\" style=\"color:#dc2626; font-weight:500;\">No hype</span>,\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-yellow\" style=\"color:#ca8a04; font-weight:500;\">no motivational nonsense</span>\n  \u2014 just <span class=\"blog-accent-green\" style=\"color:#16a34a; font-weight:500;\">real progress</span>,\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-green\" style=\"color:#16a34a; font-weight:500;\">real mistakes</span>,\n  and <span class=\"blog-accent-green\" style=\"color:#16a34a; font-weight:500;\">real takeaways</span>.\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-body\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #374151;\">\n  I\u2019m using this space to document\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-purple\" style=\"color:#7c3aed;\">projects</span>,\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-cyan\" style=\"color:#0891b2;\">experiments</span>,\n  and <span class=\"blog-accent-pink\" style=\"color:#db2777;\">ideas</span>\n  as they evolve. Some posts will be technical, some conceptual, and some just observations worth writing down.\n</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"blog-title-section\" style=\"font-size: 1.7em; margin: 28px 0 12px; color: #7c3aed;\">\n  What You\u2019ll Find Here\n</h2>\n\n<ul class=\"blog-list-main\" style=\"margin-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; color: #1f2937;\">\n  <li class=\"blog-list-item\">\n    <span class=\"blog-accent-blue\" style=\"color:#2563eb;\">Project breakdowns</span> and post-mortems\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"blog-list-item\">\n    <span class=\"blog-accent-red\" style=\"color:#dc2626;\">Hard lessons</span> learned the long way\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"blog-list-item\">\n    <span class=\"blog-accent-cyan\" style=\"color:#0891b2;\">Notes</span> on tech, systems, and problem-solving\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"blog-list-item\">\n    <span class=\"blog-accent-pink\" style=\"color:#db2777;\">Ideas</span> that are still rough but interesting\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-emphasis\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #374151;\">\n  Everything here is written\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-yellow\" style=\"color:#ca8a04; font-weight:500;\">while doing the work</span>,\n  not after pretending it was obvious.\n</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"blog-title-section-green\" style=\"font-size: 1.7em; margin: 28px 0 12px; color: #16a34a;\">\n  Why Write in Public\n</h2>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-clarity\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #1f2937;\">\n  Writing forces\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-blue-strong\" style=\"color:#2563eb; font-weight:600;\">clarity</span>.\n  If I can\u2019t explain something simply, I don\u2019t understand it well enough.\n  This blog keeps me honest and builds a record I can come back to.\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-bonus\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #374151;\">\n  If this helps someone else\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-purple\" style=\"color:#7c3aed;\">building their own thing</span>,\n  that\u2019s a bonus.\n</p>\n\n<h2 class=\"blog-title-section-pink\" style=\"font-size: 1.7em; margin: 28px 0 12px; color: #db2777;\">\n  What\u2019s Next\n</h2>\n\n<p class=\"blog-paragraph-outro\" style=\"font-size: 1.05em; line-height: 1.8; color: #1f2937;\">\n  Posts will come as projects progress.\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-red\" style=\"color:#dc2626;\">No fixed schedule</span>,\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-yellow\" style=\"color:#ca8a04;\">no filler</span>\n  \u2014 only when there\u2019s something\n  <span class=\"blog-accent-green-strong\" style=\"color:#16a34a; font-weight:600;\">worth sharing</span>.\n</p>\n<p class=\"disclaimer\" style=\"color:blue;\">Note : \"This was made by chatgpt btw\"</p>",
